WEBVTT

00:00:17.050 --> 00:00:20.100
"Episode 6: Grandpa Hearts Futaba"

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.560
"Episode 6: Grandpa Hearts Futaba"
What are you looking at?

00:00:22.930 --> 00:00:28.190
I got a text from Grand-- my grandfather.

00:00:28.190 --> 00:00:29.980
Really?

00:00:29.980 --> 00:00:31.780
"G: I put them on display
again this year"
Hina dolls?

00:00:31.780 --> 00:00:35.280
"G: I put them on display
again this year"
