00:01:25.370 --> 00:01:26.750
"G: Who the heck is he!!!"
"G: What rock did he
crawl out from under."

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:27.750
"G: Hey! You never told me"

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:29.880
"G: Hey! You never told me"
"G: about this guy!!"
That's strange. Sounds like he's mad...

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:31.960
"G: I've cared for you from birth!!
He doesn't know how long you wet the bed."

