come with me or anything...

00:03:39.300 --> 00:03:44.510
Well, I figured as long as you were going,
I'd tag along. What about you, Igarashi?

00:03:44.510 --> 00:03:48.970
I'm here to get myself a birthday present.

00:03:48.970 --> 00:03:51.850
What?! Today's your birthday?!

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:55.400
Yes. Why do you ask?

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.900
It's my birthday, too.

00:03:57.900 --> 00:03:59.730
Huh?

00:03:59.730 --> 00:04:01.070
No way!

00:04:01.070 --> 00:04:03.450
Yeah, is that incredible or what?

00:04:03.450 --> 00:04:08.330
Tell you what, I'll get you your gift
if you get me mine, okay?

00:04:08.330 --> 00:04:09.290
What?

00:04:09.290 --> 00:04:13.460
You can just get me whatever.
And I'll do the same for you.

00:04:13.460 --> 00:04:15.130
Huh...?

00:04:15.130 --> 00:04:18.880
