00:04:40.230 --> 00:04:41.480
Come on, let's do this.

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:42.570
Sure!

00:04:47.530 --> 00:04:51.080
--Happy birthday to you!
--Happy birthday!

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:58.170
Um... Thank you.

00:04:58.170 --> 00:05:02.050
Same here! I'll take good care of them.

00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:06.340
Come on, we're going.

00:05:06.340 --> 00:05:08.970
Sure, let's go get something to eat.

00:05:23.110 --> 00:05:25.400
Here comes a real tough guy.

00:05:25.400 --> 00:05:27.360
No, it can't be...

00:05:33.830 --> 00:05:36.750
Happy birthday, Futaba!

00:05:46.090 --> 00:05:47.630
Who the heck are you?

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:51.300
Hey!

00:05:51.300 --> 00:05:53.810
