She belongs to no one.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:10.660
Who <i>are </i>you, anyway?

00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:13.200
He's my grandfather.

00:06:13.200 --> 00:06:15.580
What? This jerk?

00:06:15.580 --> 00:06:17.790
Who are you calling a jerk?

00:06:17.790 --> 00:06:21.710
Futaba, who <i>is </i>this jerk?
What rock did he crawl out from under?

00:06:21.710 --> 00:06:24.460
Hey, what gives <i>you</i>
the right to call me a jerk?

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:28.010
