00:06:29.590 --> 00:06:30.970
What's going on?

00:06:30.970 --> 00:06:33.220
Those are two huge guys.

00:06:33.220 --> 00:06:35.600
Hey, it's kind of embarrassing
for you to be doing that here,

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:37.140
so can't we take this somewhere else?

00:06:37.140 --> 00:06:38.640
"Itoguruma"

00:06:42.940 --> 00:06:44.940
I don't care if you <i>are </i>Futaba's <i>senpai</i>,

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:48.530
you've got no business taking
pictures of just you and her.

00:06:48.530 --> 00:06:52.490
Oh, you mean that picture we took for fun?

00:06:52.490 --> 00:06:55.870
What? Are you toying with Futaba?

00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:58.660
Huh? What the heck are you talking about?

00:06:58.660 --> 00:07:00.250
Hey!

00:07:00.250 --> 00:07:03.540
Futaba's <i>my </i>adorable little granddaughter!

00:07:03.540 --> 00:07:07.630
Igarashi's <i>my </i>trusty <i>kouhai</i>!

00:07:13.090 --> 00:07:16.510
You think you can put your hand
on Futaba's head without asking?

00:07:16.510 --> 00:07:18.520
You saying I can't?

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:22.560
I'm the only one who's allowed
to pat Futaba on the head!

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:23.900
What?!

00:07:36.620 --> 00:07:40.410
Futaba, have you been hanging out
with that big lug these days?

00:07:40.410 --> 00:07:41.620
What?

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:46.250
I came all this way to celebrate
your birthday, Futaba, and you...

00:07:46.250 --> 00:07:48.590
Grandpa's very unhappy.

00:07:48.590 --> 00:07:54.930
Wh... What are you talking about? I told
you Takeda-<i>senpai</i>'s a <i>senpai </i>from work!

00:07:54.930 --> 00:07:57.680
Are you two in <i>that </i>kind of relationship?

00:07:57.680 --> 00:08:02.100
What?! I've had it! If you
keep on saying stuff like that,

00:08:02.100 --> 00:08:04.190
then you should just go home!

00:08:06.060 --> 00:08:09.650
Oh, Futaba...

00:08:10.610 --> 00:08:12.740
"39 (Thank You) Ice Cream"

00:08:12.740 --> 00:08:14.530
Natsumi!

00:08:15.570 --> 00:08:19.580
Futaba, sorry it's a day late, but...
Happy birthday!

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:21.160
Thanks.

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:22.830
Whatever you want, it's my treat!

00:08:22.830 --> 00:08:27.670
Sweet! Then, I want some cake.
I didn't get to eat any yesterday.

00:08:27.670 --> 00:08:29.210
Oh, really?

00:08:36.260 --> 00:08:40.770
Oh, my aching head...
Guess I drank too much...

00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:45.060
Huh? Futaba? Where are you? Futaba!

00:08:46.230 --> 00:08:49.360
Surely she didn't go out
on a date with that big lug...

00:08:50.610 --> 00:08:53.110
"I'm going out to meet Natsumi.
--Futaba"

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:57.280
Natsumi-<i>chan</i>? Really?

00:09:02.370 --> 00:09:06.040
She'd hate me for asking...

00:09:09.420 --> 00:09:11.500
--I don't understand the way
Futaba's been thinking lately...

00:09:11.500 --> 00:09:13.050
--What a plot twist, huh?
--I don't understand the way
Futaba's been thinking lately...

00:09:13.050 --> 00:09:15.010
It really blew me away!

