I never would've thought
their love would be so pure.

00:09:39.070 --> 00:09:44.290
So, young ladies these days trade places
with guys in their dreams, huh?

00:09:46.830 --> 00:09:53.550
Now I kind of understand.
I can rest easy for now.

00:09:53.550 --> 00:09:59.260
Wait. Hold on... So that's why
she's been so cold to me lately...

00:10:01.930 --> 00:10:04.390
