00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:11.360
It's from Grandpa.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.190
He must really love you.

00:10:14.570 --> 00:10:17.570
"G: Who are you?"

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:25.830
"G: Who are you?"

00:10:26.330 --> 00:10:30.170
I guess she's out on a date
with that big lug after all...

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:35.340
What are <i>you </i>looking at?

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:37.880
What the heck are <i>you </i>doing here?

00:10:41.140 --> 00:10:45.390
Oh, so <i>this </i>is where you've been!
Well, I'll be!

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:49.440
What are you babbling about?

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:55.570
Looks like I've finally caught one!

00:11:28.310 --> 00:11:30.100
Um...

00:11:32.940 --> 00:11:36.320
