00:11:38.280 --> 00:11:39.860
"Batting Center"

00:11:39.860 --> 00:11:43.200
Oh, I haven't done this in a while...

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:13.600
Wow...

00:12:13.810 --> 00:12:14.940
"Cheese Umeebou"
"Crispy & Delicious"

00:12:15.150 --> 00:12:17.480
Thanks guys!

00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:19.780
Can I get my prizes, please?

00:12:19.780 --> 00:12:24.320
Oh, I'm sorry. I'm all out of prizes...

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.070
No way!

00:12:30.950 --> 00:12:32.710
"Itomaki Ramen"

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:38.920
Oh, Harumi! You free? I bet you are!

00:12:44.970 --> 00:12:49.010
The shopping center has us doing this
volunteer work. Thanks for pitching in!

00:12:49.010 --> 00:12:51.430
Oh, it's no big deal.

00:12:55.980 --> 00:12:57.440
It's him...

00:12:57.440 --> 00:13:00.190
If you don't mind, could you help us out?

00:13:15.210 --> 00:13:16.580
Hey, what's the big idea?

00:13:16.580 --> 00:13:18.750
It's first come, first served.

00:13:20.380 --> 00:13:24.130
I've collected this much already.

00:13:24.130 --> 00:13:25.510
Same here.

00:13:47.410 --> 00:13:50.530
Hey, Harumi, how are things go--?

00:14:04.630 --> 00:14:07.380
Hey, nice work there.

00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:10.890
Same to you.

00:14:14.310 --> 00:14:16.100
Cheers!

00:14:20.610 --> 00:14:24.650
For a man with your looks,
you're a pretty okay guy!

00:14:24.650 --> 00:14:26.700
You're one to talk.

00:14:26.700 --> 00:14:28.530
That's for sure!

00:14:37.790 --> 00:14:39.080
"G: Who are you?"

00:14:39.080 --> 00:14:40.670
"G: Who are you?"
Futaba...

00:14:41.290 --> 00:14:43.880
You're really crazy about
your granddaughter, huh?

00:14:43.880 --> 00:14:45.880
Of course I am.

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:52.800
Futaba... Futaba...
was such an adorable kid!

00:14:55.180 --> 00:14:57.100
Futaba!

00:14:57.100 --> 00:14:59.100
Futaba!

00:15:01.400 --> 00:15:02.230
"Futaba: Age 6"

00:15:02.230 --> 00:15:03.440
"Futaba: Age 6"
Hello, Grandpa!

00:15:03.980 --> 00:15:07.110
Grandpa's home!

00:15:08.110 --> 00:15:09.110
You happy to see me?

00:15:09.110 --> 00:15:10.950
Yeah, but you smell kind of funny.

00:15:10.950 --> 00:15:13.320
You're happy, huh? That's great!

00:15:16.490 --> 00:15:20.040
Futaba, I'm home! Where are you?

00:15:21.170 --> 00:15:21.920
Hello, Grandpa. Um, Grandpa?

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:24.500
"Futaba: Age 8"

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:24.500
Hello, Grandpa. Um, Grandpa?

00:15:24.500 --> 00:15:26.300
"Futaba: Age 8"

00:15:24.500 --> 00:15:26.300
Yes? What is it?

00:15:27.880 --> 00:15:30.180
I got a hundred on my test.

00:15:30.180 --> 00:15:34.390
Really? Way to go, Granddaughter!

00:15:34.390 --> 00:15:38.560
Hey, stop it! Only kids
get their hair tousled.

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:40.640
