treating you to a meal today.

00:19:04.010 --> 00:19:06.220
See you later.

00:19:06.220 --> 00:19:09.270
That's right. Today's White Day.

00:19:09.270 --> 00:19:10.350
"Strawberry Candy"

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:13.230
He remembered...

00:19:17.690 --> 00:19:19.360
So, what do you want to have?

00:19:19.360 --> 00:19:21.610
Let me think...

00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:26.750
Sorry, first I've got to take a leak...

00:19:26.750 --> 00:19:28.910
In that case, I'll hold your briefcase.

00:19:28.910 --> 00:19:30.620
Thanks!

00:19:30.620 --> 00:19:32.580
I'll be right back!

00:19:37.420 --> 00:19:41.340
Ohhh, I almost wet my pants.

00:19:42.340 --> 00:19:44.470
What the heck are <i>you </i>doing here?!

00:19:44.470 --> 00:19:47.350
It was just a coincidence.
A coincidence, I tell you!

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:51.270
"Keep Our Restroom Clean"

00:19:51.270 --> 00:19:52.480
Hey...

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:53.770
Yeah?

00:19:53.770 --> 00:19:57.190
Is Futaba doing a good job at work?

00:19:58.780 --> 00:20:01.400
