for asking strange questions.

00:20:04.660 --> 00:20:07.790
In a weird way, you're kind of a sissy!

00:20:07.790 --> 00:20:12.870
She's doing a fine job. She's also pretty
headstrong, like <i>somebody </i>here.

00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:19.920
We were just about to go get
something to eat. Come join us.

00:20:21.510 --> 00:20:24.430
W-Well, I'll be...

00:20:24.430 --> 00:20:26.720
Hey, stop it!

00:20:26.720 --> 00:20:30.640
What's a little kid like you doing
wearing a business suit?

00:20:30.640 --> 00:20:31.390
Wh...

00:20:31.390 --> 00:20:36.230
Wait, don't tell me you're actually a
businesswoman. That's hysterical!

00:20:36.230 --> 00:20:38.530
Seriously?

00:20:38.530 --> 00:20:40.690
Hey now, don't cry.

00:20:40.690 --> 00:20:43.820
It makes it look like we're
doing something mean.

00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:49.040
Come on, stop crying.

00:20:49.040 --> 00:20:51.540
There's a good girl...

00:20:57.090 --> 00:21:00.170
Hey, who said you could touch her?

00:21:02.590 --> 00:21:05.680
What's this? Daddy's come to the rescue?

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:09.390
He's just acting tough
in front of his kid.

00:21:13.390 --> 00:21:14.730
Hey.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:20.480
You guys got it all wrong.

00:21:22.780 --> 00:21:26.780
<i>Grandpa's </i>come to the rescue, <i>punks</i>!

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:34.370
I'm sorry!

00:21:34.370 --> 00:21:38.340
Please, don't apologize. I wasn't hurt.

00:21:38.340 --> 00:21:41.630
My granddaughter's got a heart of gold...

00:21:41.630 --> 00:21:44.630
What are you doing here, Grandpa?

00:21:44.630 --> 00:21:50.060
Even though we were here, we couldn't
shield you from that awful experience...

00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:53.270
I said, "What are you
doing here, Grandpa?"

00:21:53.270 --> 00:21:57.440
Futaba, you must've been scared...

00:21:57.440 --> 00:22:04.570
Whenever you feel like crying,
you can cry in Grandpa's arms anytime!

00:22:07.570 --> 00:22:11.530
Well, what can you do, I guess.

00:22:11.530 --> 00:22:16.750
All right, let's go get something to eat.
You too, Gramps.

00:22:16.750 --> 00:22:19.500
Grandpa, what do you want to have?

00:22:19.500 --> 00:22:21.170
Futaba...

00:23:54.600 --> 00:23:59.520
"Illustration: Onodera-san"
